(1, 'This book surprised me.  I expected to like it – I enjoy vampire and paranormal fiction.  And yet I didn’t think I would like it as much as I did.', '2014-07-02 06:14:00.742000000', '5', 1),
(3, 'The pace of the story is good and the book itself is well-written.  The characters are engaging, and the main ones, Claire, Eve, Michael and Shane are likeable.', '2018-07-10 03:10:00.742000000', '4.5', 1),
(2, 'If you enjoy vampire novels, you will probably enjoy this, but be warned it is aimed at teenagers / young adults.  Adult themes are kept to a minimum, and gore levels are also low.', '2019-12-10 07:10:00.742000000', '5', 1),
(1, 'Author Deaver is just as cunning and deceptive as his killer.', '2019-06-1 09:10:00.722000000', '4', 16);

